{"tid":1493879,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[心理戰part2] 激進警員又打人 白衫又亂講嘢得罪人","createTime":"2019-08-21T12:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T02:45:41.000Z","uid":28759,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"733c0142c7338a043450dd789d1bc5d69f75a479","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"上個 post︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a><br />\n<br />\n分化警隊範文︰<br />\n<br />\n搞個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記者會</strong></span>都搞唔掂<br />\n架<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">水炮車</span></strong>咁耐都未落場原來漏水<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">白衫</span></strong>又唔撚俾人用催淚彈<br />\n問<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公安</span></strong>借人又俾人發現<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">臥底</span></strong>扮示威者嗰班又係柒<br />\n去廁所換衫先返入警總都唔識<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反黑</span></strong>嗰班可唔可以醒少少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>doj</strong></span> 又包庇啲害群之馬<br />\n警隊形象咪繼續插水囉<br />\n原本學生運動搞到依家全民參與咁<br />\n啲警嫂依家都唔敢同人講條仔當差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話個仔返學俾人欺凌點算<br />\n一日最衰都係班<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文官</strong></span>搞埋啲逃犯條例<br />\n無啦啦搞壇嘢出嚟<br />\n好心冇諮詢就唔好夾硬嚟啦<br />\n啲人上街反對又搞著警隊<br />\n再咁落去真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>俾佢地搞死</strong></span><br />\n依家行咇都會俾人問候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次話警方/政府柒<br />\n要指明係邊一 group 人搞事<br />\n人就好自私嘅<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關自己事嘅批評就好易入腦</span></span></strong><br />\n就算未必認同全篇<br />\n總有一兩句佢有同感<br />\n<br />\n如果有個香港人喺日本出醜<br />\n「港人遊日隨地吐痰」<br />\n「港嬸遊日隨地吐痰」<br />\n前者你可能扮睇唔到就算<br />\n或者你會死撐又係新移民累事<br />\n後者你好可能就會加把口<br />\n鬧埋一份甚至起佢底<br />\n<br />\n因為「你」唔係「港嬸」<br />\n你唔會第一時間反駁呢句嘢<br />\n易入口好多<br />\n甚至你會認同<br />\n「係囉啲港嬸真係影衰香港」<br />\n咁就用一句嘢分化咗港嬸呢個 label 出嚟<br />\n（港女、港男、港孩）<br />\n<br />\n中国都係<br />\n啲支那人真係好柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣你就攻擊緊全部人<br />\n一個普通中国人就會起鋼啦<br />\n<br />\n啲富二代真係好柒<br />\n中国移民柒出國際<br />\n福建黑幫又搞事<br />\n小粉紅真係好嘔心<br />\n咁樣講呢<br />\n一個普通中国人可能就加把口<br />\n一齊反富二代中国移民小粉紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00771f7ed1049fbc480795fced16a4f4f282ee32","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364a89b62318df7be1afe57bc7f1bbc9e031aaa2","tid":1493879,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6314f399fc2a2e04b261d37f5a436553c04eb506","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"幫手推下 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4ea5fed15ad4fbeacdd41d199d2b1018eb5129","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0752c5b267a992bde09fb7e95ea37216ce8286be","tid":1493879,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d702d59e9069a69097c2b6563ae48b07b0154a1","tid":1493879,"uid":311177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dca5b50233ebd56bf2b681febdb80c47f9d54b90","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584659712a9ce6465b78c84dcf9c570bf1dca266","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗班差佬</span></strong>又玩警黑合作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb113fb699431ce6ef65843b868ccdc393dd7b7","tid":1493879,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"文宣啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7138ef94645eab906a5a81dd6ec96c77d6f9207c","tid":1493879,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"歡迎警察捉供有力證據指出政府私插中國特警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494459</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e004ca737c5d3811f2416275944373f1d6bd92f","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42018e90ba358cb4125b68c07b2e1489bef295c2","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df14c685efaf15cd2139ec39e9f54c3b05934f26","tid":1493879,"uid":288786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"評論白兵的一點短視<br />\nYouTube嘅白兵及其朋友白兵頭係我非常佩服的分析能力極高的青年KOL，各位如果未聽過他們的video就一定要聽聽：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eif-Fe6_UAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Feif-Fe6_UAw&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9omdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=b3b9bbd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eif-Fe6_UAw</a>  <br />\n<br />\n香港有白兵這樣的青年才俊，香港的前途無可限量。但是白兵有時候刻意與和理非及泛民割席，這雖然有其可接受的理據：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwS0PDYcWh8U&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9omdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=5e33d6c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wS0PDYcWh8U</a><br />\n就顯示了年輕人一些短視。因為後來有網友問白兵這場運動最後如何勝出呢？白兵沒能提供一個好的答覆。請恕我淺薄提供一些觀點給白兵及其聽眾參考：<br />\n<br />\n1.年輕人急於求成往往忽略了要長期地全方位地對抗。八十年代九十年代的香港年輕人也曾為香港前途激烈抗爭（其激烈程度由前港督尤德在北京心臟病亡可証），當年的年輕人現在的中年人一直都有通過議會選舉、71遊行、64集會等抗爭，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請傘後一代不要放棄這些戰場</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n2.年輕人可能會對中共的惡魔本質瞭解不深，雖然爭取真普選是<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">與虎謀皮</span></span>，但是只要全方位錙銖必較（請參考以下幾點），一定可以玩殘十幾億人的老虎加跳蚤的。<br />\n<br />\n3.中共計劃用深圳取代香港，這是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個好機會趕走香港的親中財團，他們放棄香港自然就不會為其利益而介意香港人自主</span></span>。香港人要趁機說服歐美如果中共不給予香港真普選，歐美要制裁香港的親中財團的產品，同時培植和不制裁香港的<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反共經濟</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n4.香港的反共經濟可以在各行各業包括金融及新經濟同歐美同行建立緊密聯繫，要建立全球網絡，可借助全球各地的香港移民。<br />\n<br />\n5.香港的反共經濟要有百萬人或更多人參與，要有自己的產業規劃，要有市場文宣，要更多更快地使用人工智能等等新科技，要利用與深圳的就近地理位置借鑒深圳的成功經驗。<br />\n<br />\n6.香港人要為反共經濟作出長期的抗爭，因為會被中共及親中財團打壓，因此要在區議會、立法會、選委會中爭取每一票。不要過於依賴某些歐美政治人物，要依賴歐美市場及在歐美經濟轉型中的各種需要。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span>心"},{"pid":"4ab6193a1333b47de2bc42ec794583f6ac6e2b6a","tid":1493879,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}